                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A slithering pit is so clear it's difficult to spot. A successful @Check[type:perception|dc:30] check is required to notice a stationary slithering pit, and a creature must be @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Search]{Searching} to attempt this check.</p>\n<p>A creature that walks into the pit's space might fall into any pit currently in effect due to Dimensional Pit.</p>"
